@startuml
title SE Admin DuLieuDuKhach
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam monochrome true
hide footbox
actor Admin as A
participant "app.js\nloadTouristOverview()" as FE
participant "app.js\napi(url, options)" as APIJS
participant "Program.cs\nGET /api/tourists/overview" as API1
participant "Program.cs\nGET /api/tourists/poi-scan-dashboard" as API2
database "TravelGuideDb\nGetTouristOverviewAsync()" as DB1
database "TravelGuideDb\nGetTouristPoiScanDashboardAsync()" as DB2
A -> FE : Tab dữ liệu du khách / refresh
FE -> APIJS : await api(`/api/tourists/overview?visitHistoryChartWeekStart=...`)
APIJS -> API1 : GET
API1 -> DB1 : await GetTouristOverviewAsync(visitHistoryChartWeekStart)
DB1 --> API1 : object dashboard
FE -> APIJS : await api(/api/tourists/poi-scan-dashboard)
APIJS -> API2 : GET
API2 -> DB2 : await GetTouristPoiScanDashboardAsync()
DB2 --> API2 : object dashboard quét POI
FE --> A : render KPI / bảng / biểu đồ

note right of API2
  GET /api/tourists/poi-scan-dashboard
  cũng được gọi từ tab Heatmap
  (app.js refreshHeatmapTab),
  không chỉ tab Dữ liệu du khách.
end note
@enduml
